                       java.lang.String modell,
                       java.lang.String bicycleStatus,
                       double price_of_bike,
                       int nr)
        method registers bicycles into the database
        Parameters:
        make - the maker of the bicycle, for examble DBS or Diamant
        modell - the model of the bicycle, a combobox given on the GUI
        bicycleStatus - the status of the bicycle. it will automatically be 'in storage'
        price_of_bike - how much the bike cost at purchase
        nr - how many bicycles you want to register of the same make, model and price
